{
  "stem": "17426.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were glad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At least our life will continue as it did in Gutenbrunn, as it did in Steineck, miserable as it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But some of us will continue living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then soon we saw as the daylight broke, people in striped suits, in zebra suits and striped hats of the same material.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we didn't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we were still wearing civilian clothes in the labor camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of them signaled to us, by putting his hand over his neck and sliding it across, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which could only mean nothing good is awaiting us, that our life is over.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then as we were slowly pushed forwards by the cars, by the locomotive, we saw others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they raised their hands up in the air, to show strength.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so we took their signal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we knew that nothing good is awaiting us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But this may be our survival.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And soon, the car stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the doors slid open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And chaos broke-- the SS men with their dogs, with their whips, yelling, [SPEAKING GERMAN], leave everything on the rails.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I left everything that I had-- my little satchel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I kept my dental instruments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I thought they had kept me alive so long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Perhaps they will have a chance to keep me alive again, here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But an SS man came over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he pushed his whip at-- at me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, what is in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I told him those are dental instruments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, [GERMAN], leave behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, those are dental instruments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I use them in camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
